nbrenner and star outfielder Reggie Jackson.}}</ref><ref name=abtwboom>{{cite magazine |url=https://vault.si.com/vault/1978/07/31/a-bunt-that-went-boom-for-bunting-when-manager-billy-martin-ordered-him-to-swing-away-reggie-jackson-was-suspended-and-so-began-a-chain-of-tumultuous-events-that-culminated-in-martins-resignation |magazine=Sports Illustrated |last=Keith |first=Larry |title=A bunt that went boom! |date=1978-07-31 |page=14 |access-date=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101101607/https://vault.si.com/vault/1978/07/31/a-bunt-that-went-boom-for-bunting-when-manager-billy-martin-ordered-him-to-swing-away-reggie-jackson-was-suspended-and-so-began-a-chain-of-tumultuous-events-that-culminated-in-martins-resignation |dead-url=no }}</ref>。洋基隊全明星賽後的五場就輸了四場，還包括在主場三連戰被{{le|1978年堪薩斯皇家隊球季|1978 Kansas City Royals season|皇家隊}}橫掃，主力瑞吉·傑克森更遭到禁賽<ref name=dyrjsus>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=WQsiAAAAIBAJ&pg=997%2C2864936 |work=The Day |location=New London, Connecticut |agency=Associated Press |title=Reggie Jackson suspended |date=1978-07-18 |page=19 |accessdate=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2021-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210617061808/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=WQsiAAAAIBAJ&pg=997%2C2864936 }}</ref><ref name=ergbgoat>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=QMhYAAAAIBAJ&pg=3334%2C4963897 |work=Eugene Register-Guard |location=Oregon |agency=Associated Press |title=Billy's goat |date=1978-07-18 |page=1C |accessdate=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317093026/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=QMhYAAAAIBAJ&pg=3334%2C4963897 }}</ref>；他們的勝率在7月19日早晨時只有{{Winning percentage|47|42|record=y}}，遠遠落後紅襪隊達14場勝差<ref name=stjul18/><ref>{{harvnb|Frommer|Frommer|2004|p=38}}</ref><ref name=bbsal>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=CfZLAAAAIBAJ&pg=6941%2C1482207 |work=Spokesman-Review |location=Spokane, Washington 