|work=Nashua Telegraph |location=New Hampshire |agency=UPI |last=Madden |first=Bill |title=Red Sox finally break Yankee winning streak |date=1978-09-18 |page=21 |accessdate=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317093133/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=JBNSAAAAIBAJ&pg=5194%2C3750542 }}</ref><ref name=bossvthr>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=xvlVAAAAIBAJ&pg=6472%2C5399821 |work=Eugene Register-Guard |location=Oregon |agency=wire service reports |title=Boston 7-3 |date=1978-09-18 |page=4D |accessdate=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2021-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210617061809/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=xvlVAAAAIBAJ&pg=6472%2C5399821 }}</ref><ref name=sdhbbty>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=s_ZLAAAAIBAJ&pg=3287%2C1558410 |work=Spokesman-Review |location=Spokane, Washington |agency=Associated Press |title=Scott's double helps Bosox beat Yanks, hang in chase |date=1978-09-18 |page=21 |accessdate=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317093200/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=s_ZLAAAAIBAJ&pg=3287%2C1558410 }}</ref>，紅襪隊不但取勝，還在未來兩周拉出12勝2敗的高潮，並成功在洋基隊賽程剩下七場時，追成一場勝差。洋基隊雖然拉出六連勝<ref name=mygfiat>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5JczAAAAIBAJ&pg=6769%2C144515 |work=Eugene Register-Guard |location=Oregon |agency=wire service reports |title='Miracle' Yanks go for it all today |date=1978-10-01 |page=7B |accessdate=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317093152/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5JczAAAAIBAJ&pg=6769%2C144515 }}</ref>，但卻於10月1日星期日最後一場在自家主場面對{{le|1978年克里夫蘭印地安人隊球季|1978 Cleveland Indians season|印地安人隊}}時輸球<ref name="FinalGames"/><ref name=rwgsac>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=3AZSAAAAIBAJ&pg=5513%2C192978 |work=Nashua Telegraph |location=New Hampshire |agency=UPI |last=McMane |first=Fred |title=Rick Waits gives Sox another chance |date=1978-10-02 |page=32 |accessdate=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2021-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210617061810/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=3AZSAAAAIBAJ&pg=5513%2C192978 }}</ref><ref name=wmsbcy>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=SesyAAAAIBAJ&pg=6530%2C379711 |work=Wilmington Morning Star |location=North Carolina |agency=wire reports |title=Bosox catch Yanks; playoff set today |date=1978-10-02 |page=3B |accessdate=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2021-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210617061821/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=SesyAAAAIBAJ&pg=6530%2C379711 }}</ref><ref name=ylabon>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=TM1eAAAAIBAJ&pg=3226%2C592352 |work=Lewiston Morning Tribune |location=Idaho |agency=Associated Press |title=Yankees lose a big one |date=1978-10-02 |page=5B |accessdate=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317093157/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=TM1eAAAAIBAJ&pg=3226%2C592352 }}</ref>，而紅襪隊則是最後八場全勝追上洋基隊<ref name="FinalGames"/>，芬威球場也在印地安人隊左投{{le|瑞克·維特斯|Rick Waits}}率隊9比2完投勝洋基隊後，<ref name=rwgsac/><ref name=bscynks>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=SesyAAAAIBAJ&pg=6530%2C379711 |work=Wilmington Morning Star |location=North Carolina |agency=wire reports |title=BoSox catch Yanks; playoff set today |date=1978-10-02 |page=3B |accessdate=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2021-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210617061821/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=SesyAAAAIBAJ&pg=6530%2C379711 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Indian ambush stalls yankee drive toward title|newspaper=The Globe and Mail|date=1978-10-02|page=S2}}</ref>在大螢幕上打出喜訊：「謝謝你瑞克·維特斯，明天比賽見（''THANK YOU RICK WAITS, GAME TOMORROW''）」<ref>{{harvnb|Frommer|Frommer|2004|p=48}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Waits' Big Day Gave Sox Chance|last=Goldberg|first=Jeff|newspaper=The Hartford Courant|date=2003-10-01|page=C3}}</ref>。

==比賽過程==
這是美聯自[[1948年美國聯盟龍頭決勝加賽|1948年]]以來的第一場決勝加賽，當年{{le|1948年克里夫蘭印地安人隊球季|1948 Cleveland Indians season|印地安人隊}}在芬威球場擊敗{{le|1948年波士頓紅襪隊球季|1948 Boston Red Sox season|紅襪隊}}後奪得美聯龍頭之位，同時這也是大聯盟自{{mlby|1969}}施行分區制度以來的第一場<ref name=morningrecord/>。洋基隊派出162場正規季賽中拿下24勝的吉德里先發<ref name=morningrecord>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=qjZIAAAAIBAJ&sjid=TBAJ&pg=4365,64195&dq=yankees+red+sox&hl=en ''The Morning Record and Journal''] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=qjZIAAAAIBAJ&sjid=TBAJ&pg=4365,64195&dq=yankees+red+sox&hl=en |date=20210617061811 }} via Google News Archive Search</ref>，但這次僅休息三天，比平常還要短<ref name=Lyle244>Lyle & Golenbock, p. 244</ref>；而紅襪隊則是推出托雷斯先發<ref name=morningrecord/>，他曾在{{le|開幕戰|Opening Day}}當天代表球隊先發<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=hf0sAAAAIBAJ&pg=1703,2002525&dq=yankees+red+sox&hl=en |title=Mike Torrez — Traveling Man finding job security in Boston|first=Karl|last=Gulbronsen|newspaper=The Palm Beach Post|date=1978-04-03|access-date=2012-06-18}}</ref>，並在季賽中取得16勝12敗的戰績，但紅襪隊季末的掙扎使其苦吞六連敗<ref name=morningrecord/>。比賽於10月2日[[北美東部時區|美國東部時間]]下午兩點三十分開打，全國電視轉播則是由{{le|ABC美國職棒大聯盟|Major League Baseball on ABC|ABC}}負責。

[[File:Bucky_Dent_signs_autographs.jpg|thumb]]
紅襪隊的[[卡爾·雅澤姆斯基|卡爾·雅澤姆斯基]]在二局下半打出[[陽春全壘打|陽春全壘打]]，[[吉姆·賴斯|吉姆·賴斯]]則在六局下半打出一分打點的一壘安打送回{{le|瑞克·伯勒森|Rick Burleson}}，幫助紅襪隊取得2比0領先<ref name=milwaukee/>。但七局上半一出局後風雲變色，紅襪隊的先發投手托雷斯先後被洋基隊的[[克里斯·錢布里斯|克里斯·錢布里斯]]和[[羅伊·懷特|羅伊·懷特]]各擊出一支一壘安打，雖然讓下一棒{{le|吉姆·斯賓塞|Jim Spencer}}擊出飛球出局<ref>{{harvnb|Shaughnessy|1990|p=144}}</ref>，但輪到登特打擊時，他一棒將球打到左外野[[綠色怪物|綠色怪物]]的大牆外，變成一支三分全壘打，使得戰局逆轉，由洋基隊取得3比2領先<ref>{{harvnb|Frommer|Frommer|2004|p=178}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Yankee power KIs Bosox hopes|last=Patton|first=Paul|newspaper=The Globe and Mail|date=1978-10-03|page=P37}}</ref>。

托雷斯在保送{{le|米奇·里弗斯|Mickey Rivers}}後退場，由[[中繼投手|中繼投手]]{{le|鮑伯·史丹利|Bob Stanley (baseball)}}接替投球。在里弗斯盜上二壘後，[[瑟曼·蒙森|瑟曼·蒙森]]又用二壘安打一棒將前者送回得分<ref name=Lyle244/>。到了八局上半，[[瑞吉·傑克森_(棒球運動員)|瑞吉·傑克森]]的陽春全壘打錦上添花，比數拉開到5比2<ref name=Lyle244/>。然而紅襪隊八局下半就展開反攻，面對洋基隊[[終結者_(棒球)|終結者]][[戈斯·戈沙基|戈斯·戈沙基]]的投球，[[弗瑞德·林恩|弗瑞德·林恩]]和雅澤姆斯基各打出一支一分打點一壘安打讓比賽再次回到一分差<ref name=Lyle245>Lyle & Golenbock, p. 245</ref>。但洋基隊最終能成功守下紅襪的反撲，有一部份要歸功於右外野手[[盧·皮涅拉|盧·皮涅拉]]九局下半機警的防守表現：當時是一出局伯勒森在一壘，{{le|傑里·雷米|Jerry Remy}}打出右外野平飛球，可是皮涅拉卻因傍晚陽光的照射而無法看清球使其落地。然而他卻表現出很正常防守的樣子，拍了一下手套後將反彈球輕鬆接進手套。這讓伯勒森被擋在了二壘，導致下一棒賴斯打出外野深遠飛球時，前者也只能推進到三壘而非跑回追平分。<ref name=milwaukee/><ref name=Lyle245 />

此時紅襪隊兩出局兩人在壘，輪到雅澤姆斯基上場打擊，但他擊出三壘方向界外區的飛球，被洋基隊三壘手[[克雷格·奈托斯|克雷格·奈托斯]]接殺抓到最後一個出局數，洋基隊以5比4拿下這場勝利。吉德里拿下勝投後勝率來到了{{winning percentage|25|3|record=y}}，而托雷斯則是吞下敗投，同時戈沙基則取得第27次救援成功。<ref name="LineScore"/>

