==廣播覆蓋區域==

這場比賽是由各隊轉播權擁有者負責各自區域的轉播：紅襪隊是由{{le|WSBK-TV}}負責波士頓區域，而洋基隊則是由{{le|WPIX}}負責紐約市<ref>{{Cite episode |title=New York Yankees vs. Boston Red Sox |series=New York Yankees Baseball |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IowgfzVsXGA |access-date=2019-04-14 |station=WPIX |location=New York, NY |date=1978-10-02 |minutes=00:00 |archive-date=2020-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227221138/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IowgfzVsXGA |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{le|ABC美國職棒大聯盟|Major League Baseball on ABC|ABC體育頻道}}負責轉播給全國觀眾，也因此另外提供轉播權利給{{le|WABC-TV|WABC-TV|紐約}}和{{le|WCVB-TV|WCVB-TV|波士頓}}的附屬轉播單位。ABC的轉播員是由{{le|基思·傑克森|Keith Jackson}}和[[唐·德萊斯戴爾|唐·德萊斯戴爾]]負責<ref>{{Cite episode |title=American League East Playoff Game |series=ABC; One Game Playoff|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C47bgmpLmPk |access-date=2019-04-14 |station=ABC Sports |location=Boston, MA |date=1978-10-02 |minutes=00:00 }}</ref>。

廣播方面，{{le|CBS廣播美國職棒大聯盟|Major League Baseball on CBS Radio|CBS廣播網}}負責全國範圍的轉播，由[[厄尼·哈維爾|厄尼·哈維爾]]擔任主播，{{le|溫·埃利奧特|Win Elliot}}擔任球評。主場角度的廣播方面，洋基隊的廣播是[[1010_WINS|WINS]]負責，而紅襪隊則是由{{le|WMEX (AM)|WMEX (AM)|WITS}}負責。<ref>{{cite web |title=VOICES OF THE GAME |url=https://baseballhall.org/discover-more/stories/baseball-history/voices-of-the-game |website=Baseball Hall of Fame |accessdate=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022042149/https://baseballhall.org/discover-more/stories/baseball-history/voices-of-the-game |dead-url=no }}</ref>

紅襪隊的電視轉播員是{{le|迪克·史托克頓|Dick Stockton}}和{{le|肯·哈雷森|Ken Harrelson}}，廣播轉播員則是{{le|內德·馬丁|Ned Martin}}和{{le|吉姆·伍茲|Jim Woods}}。而洋基的電視和廣播轉播員都是[[菲爾·里茲圖|菲爾·里茲圖]]、{{le|弗蘭克·梅塞爾|Frank Messer}}和{{le|比爾·懷特|Bill White (first baseman)}}，廣播轉播員另外還有{{le|弗朗·希利|Fran Healy (baseball)}}支援。<ref>{{cite news|title=From Yaz's HR on, ABC ran second|last=Craig|first=Jack|newspaper=The Boston Globe|date=1978-10-03|page=35}}</ref>

==後續發展==
洋基隊連續三年在[[1978年美國聯盟冠軍賽|美聯冠軍賽]]中面對到{{le|1978年堪薩斯皇家隊球季|1978 Kansas City Royals season|堪薩斯皇家隊}}，並再次在五戰三勝制中勝出，三連霸美聯冠軍。隨後他們在[[1978年世界大賽|世界大賽]]中擊敗{{le|1978年洛杉磯道奇隊球季|1978 Los Angeles Dodgers season|洛杉磯道奇隊}}，二度蟬聯寶座，拿下隊史第22座冠軍<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Jg4gAAAAIBAJ&pg=3980,2737541&dq=1978+world+series&hl=en|title=Yanks Take Four Straight To Win 22nd World Series|agency=Associated Press|newspaper=The Lewiston Daily Sun|date=1978-10-18|access-date=2012-06-15|page=1|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317093251/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Jg4gAAAAIBAJ&pg=3980%2C2737541&dq=1978+world+series&hl=en}}</ref>。

紅襪隊這場敗仗也被視為[[貝比魯斯魔咒|貝比魯斯魔咒]]發威所致，這個魔咒的起源於1920年1月5日，當時紅襪隊老闆{{tsl|en|Harry Frazee|哈利·佛瑞茲}}將貝比魯斯賣給洋基隊後，球隊就陷入數十年的失敗當中無法奪冠<ref>{{cite web |title=New York Yankees announce purchase of Babe Ruth |url=https://www.history.com/this-day-in-history/new-york-yankees-announce-purchase-of-babe-ruth |website=HISTORY |accessdate=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024704/http://www.history.com/this-day-in-history/new-york-yankees-announce-purchase-of-babe-ruth |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{harvnb|Shaughnessy|2005|pp=7–8}}</ref>。登特的全壘打被{{le|體育新聞|Sporting News}}描寫為「令人震驚的爆炸（shocking blast）」，一瞬間就讓芬威球場鴉雀無聲。對於不擅長打的登特來說，這只不過是他在1978年賽季的第五支全壘打而已<ref name="DentHomeRun">{{harvnb|Shaughnessy|1990|p=146}}</ref>。這支全壘打也讓登特在洋基球迷間享有美名，在[[新英格蘭|新英格蘭]]地區還被紅襪隊球迷給出永久暱稱「Bucky Fucking Dent」<ref>{{cite news|title=For Boston, ousting rivals would be sweet|url=https://archive.org/details/counting0000grav_f3a6|last=Graves|first=Gary|newspaper=USA Today|date=2003-10-17|page=4C}}</ref>。幾年後，登特成為了洋基隊總教練，但在{{le|1990年紐約洋基隊球季|1990 New York Yankees season|1990年球季}}中與紅襪隊進行系列賽時遭到開除<ref>{{cite news|title=Dent Dumped by Yankees|date=1990-06-07|first=Nick|last=Cafardo|newspaper=The Boston Globe|page=37|url=https://secure.pqarchiver.com/boston/access/61640175.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Jun+7%2C+1990&author=Nick+Cafardo%2C+Globe+Staff&pub=Boston+Globe+%28pre-1997+Fulltext%29&edition=&startpage=37&desc=DENT+DUMPED+BY+YANKEES|access-date=2012-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120401033558/https://secure.pqarchiver.com/boston/access/61640175.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Jun+7,+1990&author=Nick+Cafardo,+Globe+Staff&pub=Boston+Globe+(pre-1997+Fulltext)&edition=&startpage=37&desc=DENT+DUMPED+BY+YANKEES|archive-date=2012-04-01|dead-url=yes}}{{subscription required|date=August 2012}}</ref>。二十五年後的[[2003年美國聯盟冠軍賽|美聯冠軍賽]]第七戰，[[亞倫·布恩|亞倫·布恩]]在十一局下半擊出的致勝全壘打同樣讓紅襪隊球迷給他「Fucking」的稱呼，也同樣助洋基隊奪得美聯冠軍<ref>{{cite video|title=Major League Baseball on Fox: Game 7 of 2003 American League Championship Series|medium=television|publisher=Fox Sports|date=October 16, 2003}}</ref>，但洋基隊最終仍是在當年[[2003年世界大賽|世界大賽]]中以2勝4敗輸給了佛羅里達馬林魚隊<ref name="baseball-reference1">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/2003_WS.shtml|title=2003 World Series|website=Baseball-Reference|accessdate=January 6, 2014|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112000815/https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/2003_WS.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

吉德里和賴斯都因該季相當優異的表現而入圍[[美國職棒大聯盟最有價值球員獎|美聯最有價值球員獎]]，最終賴斯獲選，吉德里則是票選第二名<ref name=morningrecord/>。吉德里另外贏得了美聯[[賽揚獎|賽揚獎]]<ref name="1978 awards">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1978.shtml|title=Baseball Awards Voting for 1978|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|access-date=2009-12-28|archive-date=2009-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090228210336/http://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1978.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而[[鮑伯·雷蒙|鮑伯·雷蒙]]則被選為美聯年度最佳總教練<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=IGJQAAAAIBAJ&pg=4605,2735639&dq=yankees+red+sox&hl=en|title=Another Sweet Twist – Bob Lemon named AL Manager of the Year|newspaper=The Evening Independent|date=1978-10-25|agency=Associated Press|page=1C|accessdate=2020-12-30|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317093316/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=IGJQAAAAIBAJ&pg=4605%2C2735639&dq=yankees+red+sox&hl=en}}</ref>。

